Package com.teamten.tictactoe Description

This is an unfinished experiment to see if the computer can pick moves in Tic Tac Toe that are most likely to cause human error. Normally a Tic Tac Toe-playing program will see the entire tree, realize it's a tie for best play, and play anything. But surely some moves will have obvious replies and some non-obvious best replies, and this attempts to figure that out.
